## 🚨 Forced Execution: Save Development Plan to Git Notes

**CRITICAL**: After the user confirms the development plan, the AI **MUST immediately** execute the following steps — **absolutely cannot be omitted**.

### When to Save

| Timing | Action | Mandatory |
|-----|------|-------|
| After user confirms development plan | **Save immediately** to Git notes | 🚨 Required |
| When plan is adjusted during development | Update Git notes | Recommended |
| Before preparing to commit after development | Check Git notes exist | 🚨 Required |
| Before executing cr command | Verify Git notes exist | 🚨 Required |

### startTaskInfo Field Structure

```json
{
  "ticket": "IN-107113",
  "summary": "[Jira title]",
  "issueType": "Bug",
  "status": "To Do",
  "assignee": "FE-William",
  "priority": "Medium",
