## Notes

1. **User confirmation first**: Commit and MR operations must be executed only after user confirms the report
2. **Report type matching**: Must generate corresponding report content based on Jira card type
3. **Final version principle**: Development plan and report must be based on the final confirmed version
4. **Automated handling**: AI independently completed projects must auto-add AI label and report when creating MR
5. **Completeness requirement**: Bug reports must include all four additional items; Request reports must include all three additional items
6. **Impact analysis**: Potential impact risk report must objectively assess and must not omit important risks
7. **Traceability requirement**: "Causing Ticket" in Bug reports must trace back to specific commits or MRs as much as possible
